title: Schedule A Tour-Newly Renovated Apartment Homes And Luxury Amenities!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Over 20,000 Sq Ft of Amenities!', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
